snippet: The University of Utah suspended its swimming coach, Greg Winslow, because of an investigation of sexual abuse allegations of underage female swimmers.
abstract: University of Utah suspends swimming coach Greg Winslow because of investigation into allegations that he sexually abused underage female swimmers.
